# 📖 What is Time & Work?

Time & Work is used to calculate:

- How much work one person completes in one day.
- How long two or more people take to finish a job together.

The most important idea is:

```text
One-Day Work = 1 / Number of Days
```

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

# 🧠 Basic Formula

## One-Day Work

```text
One-Day Work

=

1

────────────

Number of Days
```

Example

If A completes a work in **8 days**

```text
One-Day Work = 1/8
```

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

